Sir '''Vincent Litchfield Raven''' [[Knight Commander of the Order of the British Empire|KBE]] ([[3 December]] [[1858]]-[[14 February]] [[1934]]) was [[chief mechanical engineer]] of the [[North Eastern Railway (UK)|North Eastern Railway]] from 1910 to 1922.

== References ==

* ''Sir Vincent Raven, and the North Eastern Railway'' (2005) by Peter Grafton ISBN 0-85361-640-X

